  "detailed_description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the vast emptiness of space, your ship encounters an asteroid storm. Whether you survive depends on whether you can protect the cockpit.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple controls: Use the mouse to aim and shoot the energy cannon to destroy asteroids before they hit the ship!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the \"A\" and \"D\" keys to control the view.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A relaxing atmosphere.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two game modes included:</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endless mode to challenge your highest score!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level mode where your performance will be rated with stars!</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the vast emptiness of space, your ship encounters an asteroid storm. Whether you survive depends on whether you can protect the cockpit.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple controls: Use the mouse to aim and shoot the energy cannon to destroy asteroids before they hit the ship!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the \"A\" and \"D\" keys to control the view.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A relaxing atmosphere.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two game modes included:</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endless mode to challenge your highest score!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level mode where your performance will be rated with stars!</p></li></ul>",
